    "description": "《The Outer Worlds：凶险戈尔贡》是由Obsidian Entertainment和Private Division推出的超人气获奖科幻RPG作品的首个叙事扩展包。 <br><br>一条断臂和一则神秘消息将“没谱号”的船员引向了戈尔贡小行星，那里曾经上演过Halcyon最雄心勃勃、同时也最具灾难性的科学项目之一，如今却沦落为怪物和掠夺者的不法巢穴。富有的隐士Minnie Ambrose派船员们去打探关于Olivia Ambrose博士和她的母亲，以及因为那个注定失败的项目而失势的负责人的消息，但他们很快就卷入了一场将永远改变殖民地的惊天阴谋。 <br><br><strong>主要特色</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >阴谋与险象</h2>搜索一处废弃的“太空人之选”设施，揭开戈尔贡项目突然取消背后的谜团，并遇见一群新的角色。  <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393110/extras/75723e0c9d337c2cf523a4334b2ba836.poster.avif?t=1738037616\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393110/extras/75723e0c9d337c2cf523a4334b2ba836.webm?t=1738037616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393110/extras/75723e0c9d337c2cf523a4334b2ba836.mp4?t=1738037616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >新地点</h2>探索戈尔贡小行星的险恶山谷，遭遇一群被科技扭曲的敌人。 <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393110/extras/31835d8f80aae4a4fb2f3aed6c3aed2b.poster.avif?t=1738037616\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393110/extras/31835d8f80aae4a4fb2f3aed6c3aed2b.webm?t=1738037616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393110/extras/31835d8f80aae4a4fb2f3aed6c3aed2b.mp4?t=1738037616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >更多的高科技武器</h2>发现三件新奇的高科技武器，其中的魔灭棍（魔物湮灭神棍）是一件劲爆的全新格斗利器，能将敌人拽到附近发动近距离攻击。 <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393110/extras/e2ed58a8d4a795d5e22dd90751d47f67.poster.avif?t=1738037616\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393110/extras/e2ed58a8d4a795d5e22dd90751d47f67.webm?t=1738037616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393110/extras/e2ed58a8d4a795d5e22dd90751d47f67.mp4?t=1738037616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >更丰富的角色定制与传记</h2>更高的等级上限、额外的辅助能力和弱项、全新的装甲套装，以及现有装备的几个变种。另外，得益于新的便携式留声机音频日志，玩家还能深入发掘戈尔贡小行星的故事，揭开一场科学实验事故背后令人不齿的隐情。 <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393110/extras/959d57d61b51b1486d9f8f34d3140d5c.poster.avif?t=1738037616\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393110/extras/959d57d61b51b1486d9f8f34d3140d5c.webm?t=1738037616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393110/extras/959d57d61b51b1486d9f8f34d3140d5c.mp4?t=1738037616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《The Outer Worlds：凶险戈尔贡》是两部叙事扩展包中的第一部，可以单独购买或以折扣价随《The Outer Worlds扩展通行证》捆绑购买。  <br><br><i>需要有基于同一平台的《The Outer Worlds》本体才能运行扩展包。 </i>",
